{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"Final Year Research Log","author":"William Park"}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"f35ed8d6-d858-55b1-864a-078546994d15","excerpt":"As previously mentioned in my moodboard post, I want the feel for the app to be soft and playful. I selected the Visby Round CF typeface…","html":"<p>As previously mentioned in my moodboard post, I want the feel for the app to be soft and playful. I selected the Visby Round CF typeface because it achieves that well. It’s reasonably priced for commercial usage and it comes with a good variety of weights.</p>\n<p>For something as common as typography in apps I believe getting the feel that I wanted to achieve through the typeface is a huge win as it sets the tone for the rest of the application.</p>\n<p>\n  <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/type-d57547452af83eb6038f8ca622f627d1-e6fc4.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n  \n  <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block; ; max-width: 590px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 115.29110684580934%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    >\n      <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width: 100%; height: 100%; margin: 0; vertical-align: middle; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; box-shadow: inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;\"\n        alt=\"Typography\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/type-d57547452af83eb6038f8ca622f627d1-fb8a0.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/type-d57547452af83eb6038f8ca622f627d1-1a291.png 148w,\n/static/type-d57547452af83eb6038f8ca622f627d1-2bc4a.png 295w,\n/static/type-d57547452af83eb6038f8ca622f627d1-fb8a0.png 590w,\n/static/type-d57547452af83eb6038f8ca622f627d1-526de.png 885w,\n/static/type-d57547452af83eb6038f8ca622f627d1-fa2eb.png 1180w,\n/static/type-d57547452af83eb6038f8ca622f627d1-e6fc4.png 1563w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n      />\n    </span>\n  </span>\n  \n  </a>\n    </p>\n<p>I’m using the minor third scale (measured with <a href=\"https://type-scale.com\">type-scale</a>) with the app as it minifies the amount of scale difference between each level of the hierarchy. </p>","frontmatter":{"title":"Typography","date":"November 07, 2018"}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/typography/","previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/moodboard/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Moodboard"}},"next":null}}